@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_drpxtv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(0.64)
    v2 = 0.28
    v1 = v2
    v0 = wp.sin(((tmp + 0.99 + v2 + 0.77) - wp.cos(v0 + 0.29)))
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = tmp
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
